# Privacy Policy for [Your Game Name]

## Introduction
This Privacy Policy pertains to the game [Your Game Name] ("we", "us", "our"). This policy explains how we handle and treat user data. 

## Data Collection and Use
Our game is designed to store data locally on the user's device. We do not collect, use, or share any personal data or information. The game functions offline, and no data is transmitted off the device.

## No Data Sharing
We do not share any data with third parties because we do not collect any data. The game's performance and gameplay are self-contained and do not rely on external data processing.

## User Rights
Users have full control over their data as it is stored locally on their devices. They can manage or delete game data through their device's storage settings.

## Data Security
The security of your data is important to us but remember that no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. Since we do not collect data, the usual risks associated with data transmission and storage do not apply to our game.

## Changes to This Policy
Should we decide to change our privacy policy, we will update this page with the new information. 

## Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through [preferred contact method].

This policy is effective as of [Date].
